ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of CHRISTIAN ROBIN of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 25, 2018, in the place of Byron Neiles, whose term has expired.
